        "Name": "A Few Bumps Along the Way",
        "Client": "Hapless Trader",
        "Description": "A buddy of mine told me about this \u0022great\r\nshortcut\u0022 he found. The road was so bumpy\r\nI fell off my cart right into a cactus patch.\r\nAnd to make matters worse, a Diablos\r\nappeared out of nowhere and turned my\r\ncart into splinters... Why do these things\r\nalways happen to me!?",
